<h3> <code>portal_discussion</code> Tool </h3>

<p> This tool embodies the policies for a given CMFSite concerning
    the storage mechanisms for discussion about content.  In particular,
    this version implements the policy that replies to a piece of content
    are stored on a special "talkback" subobject of the content, and are
    threaded by it.
</p>

